Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.33,0:00:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.84,0:00:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.11,0:00:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.39,0:00:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.33,0:00:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.91,0:00:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.18,0:01:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.42,0:01:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.73,0:01:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.97,0:01:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在世的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.97,0:01:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必一定长得很美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.74,0:01:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.98,0:01:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉的那股力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.25,0:01:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就藏在你的美貌之中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.09,0:02:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第94话 四魂之玉的伪造者 上集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够让拥有它的人愿望实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.04,0:02:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且给予他力量的四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.01,0:02:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个时候开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们展开了漫长的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.58,0:02:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  一路上\N我们不断寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握有大部分\N四魂之玉碎片的奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.29,0:02:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这风吹得好舒服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.63,0:02:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为天气很好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落躲在什么地方\N都还不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的\N你们居然有心情享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吃啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从奈落失踪以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去一直躲着他的那些妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.55,0:03:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纷纷跑出来作怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直叫人忍无可忍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.59,0:03:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才要慢慢享受午餐\N调剂一下身心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你成熟一点行不行\N犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.76,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.73,0:03:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇又不像我们是大妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是个脆弱的凡人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太这么苛求是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝说你脆弱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝长大了\N开始懂得体谅别人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.28,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我又说错了什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  你没有说错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  说错话的不是我哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么大妖怪嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完立刻动身哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的空气真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连饭团也特别好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.13,0:03:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真的很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像可能是我多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.08,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然感觉到\N四魂之玉碎片好像在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这次怎么说得这么含糊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得这次\N跟以前有点不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.39,0:04:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越接近我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.67,0:04:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧  已经安全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛  臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想破坏本大爷的好事是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家伙吗  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  它肚子里面\N有四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.69,0:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.69,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这臭妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪弄来的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.20,0:05:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道我有四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不乖乖把那个臭小子\N给我交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想这么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.44,0:05:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好乖乖\N把四魂之玉碎片交出然后闪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尽管神气吧  小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.78,0:05:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你尝尝我妖力的厉害  嘿嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪有你说的了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  和说的不一样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.96,0:05:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.91,0:05:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?怎么了?啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.97,0:05:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.98,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉把四魂之玉捏碎啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.25,0:05:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的四魂之玉\N有那么容易捏碎吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.98,0:05:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它发出的气息\N的确很像四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.99,0:06:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看\N恐怕是仿制的四魂之玉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.99,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说有某些妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算制造四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以先给我一点水喝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那你请用这瓶水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只装水的瓶子还真是漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小名叫做出云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖先世世代代\N都担任神官之职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神官是做什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.73,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.03,0:06:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.03,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神官就是神社的负责人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爷爷就是做这个的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该是个巫女对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.31,0:06:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个神职工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须不断的进修学问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从知识里得到很多乐趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.05,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来就到各国去游历\N调查还有做纪录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.55,0:07:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你的事没有兴趣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道的是\N刚刚那块假玉的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我多年来专研的对象呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才知道\N关于四魂之玉的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上所有的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实都是来自四个灵魂所形成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.70,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是荒魂  和魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇魂  幸魂这四种吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这四个灵魂合而为一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就成为寄宿在\N肉体之内的心灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切是这样开始的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这以前我也听过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过老实说\N我并不是很明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那只妖怪\N为什么会有假的四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托你从这里说起好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是有人给它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.29,0:07:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁给它的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的妖怪给的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是想找人吵架  臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我没这个意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那只妖怪\N为什么要追你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.31,0:08:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为\N我看见了它们的交易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听人说有个神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以教人四魂之玉的传承
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找这个神社\N一路走到山上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知不觉迷了路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.09,0:08:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来在山上\N被我撞见有个妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.86,0:08:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正把四魂之玉\N交给刚才那个妖怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙是不是叫奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙自称蟒蛇大夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块四魂之玉还不完全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.87,0:08:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真正的四魂之玉\N马上就会出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟒蛇大夫是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.61,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说有个妖怪\N正在制作四魂之玉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所从旁听见的就是这些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都感觉不到妖怪的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.89,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪就在这附近\N交出四魂之玉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本闻不到奈落的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子这件事\N大概跟奈落没有关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么样  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有感觉到四魂之玉的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  一点都感觉不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那种感觉\N本来就没有很强烈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为那个是假的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假货的效力当然差很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.15,0:09:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我看到前面有个村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连个人都没有耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一个人影都看不到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那家伙怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  出云先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在这里干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经听人说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.11,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个神社供奉的是开国大神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空荡荡的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么开国大神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说开国大神的内心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.56,0:10:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏有奇魂跟幸魂两种灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.67,0:10:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇魂代表了智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而幸魂代表了爱  对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.71,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒魂代表的是勇\N和魂代表的是亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.08,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇  亲  智  爱这四种灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓的四魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些大道理还是少说两句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.32,0:10:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得这一带\N气氛有点不太对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.16,0:10:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆再调查一下这个村子看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我去村子四周看一看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一点线索也没发现说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.34,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.67,0:10:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.38,0:10:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳光为什么这么温暖\N却这么刺眼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳光会刺眼不是当然的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是当然的吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对我来说\N真的是很不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是不是有什么在燃烧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方\N到底离这里有多远呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的想法还真奇怪耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.63,0:11:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊  我第一次在这个时代\N遇见会这样想问题的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是让我有点感动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种想法在你老家很平常吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有夜晚来到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位出云先生\N他是个学者喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.51,0:11:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.88,0:11:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.02,0:11:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚你提到的那四种灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么勇还有什么亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.26,0:11:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说\N勇亲智跟爱这四个字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.79,0:11:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就这四个字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇就是勇气的勇\N代表勇敢的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你这么一说我就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲是亲密  亲爱的亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智是智慧的智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表任何事都了若指掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱就是爱情的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这么一说  我又更明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.18,0:12:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果像刚刚那么\N咬文嚼字的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说我都听不懂耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.75,0:12:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇的荒魂  亲的和魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智的奇魂  还有爱的幸魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这四种灵魂集合起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.33,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将它们封存在善灵\N邪灵和混沌之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.20,0:12:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以形成四魂之玉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.57,0:12:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说  我又糊涂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你先别逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是珊瑚的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.82,0:12:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会伤害你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.09,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们几个是路过的旅行者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会伤害你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.60,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来  臭妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.84,0:12:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝跟云母他们\N不是你以为的坏妖怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.47,0:13:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.31,0:13:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子出了什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.32,0:13:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有人想害你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会保护你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.86,0:13:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妖怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妖怪进了这个村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.13,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说有妖怪\N袭击你们的村子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都被妖怪带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.50,0:13:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天因为我做错事\N被我爸爸关在鸡舍里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好乖乖给我出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然\N我放火烧了你这个房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来  等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.52,0:13:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都给我抓出来\N一个也别漏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有没有躲起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.06,0:13:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我仔细地搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人\N都被妖怪抓走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么时候的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约五天以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.18,0:14:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来我一直偷偷\N躲在鸡舍里面不敢出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下终于明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么看不见半个村民了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  大家会怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么妖怪要抓走\N我爸爸妈妈他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会想要把他们给吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.07,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.31,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是为了要吃掉他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不必特地带走他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当场吃掉就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出云先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想妖怪的目的\N并不是要吃人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些妖怪又不是傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们很清楚随便袭击村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民们\N一定也会想办法反击的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点它们不会不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说妖怪活捉这些村民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为不想弄死他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说\N我爸妈他们应该不会死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家分头打探妖怪的下落吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要打跑这些妖怪才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  话又说回来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天色渐渐暗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不是\N打探妖怪下落的最佳时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.88,0:15:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会淹没一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是再美丽的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都会被淹没在黑暗之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对  就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.53,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到四魂之玉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.90,0:15:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在叫人吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本只希望可以多抓一些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.91,0:15:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连真正的\N四魂之玉碎片也出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.91,0:15:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们就是抓走我爸妈的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.98,0:15:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识相的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就乖乖把\N四魂之玉碎片交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该乖乖听话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看是你们这些妖怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.03,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是蟒蛇大夫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那些村民抓到哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.00,0:16:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师\N你的大名我听过好几次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的拿手好戏是风穴对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.44,0:16:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦?你知道的话就好办了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.51,0:16:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算肯乖乖听话了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.19,0:16:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块四魂之玉\N是邪气凝聚而成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.99,0:16:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.53,0:16:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸入这股邪气对你们人类来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.36,0:16:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟中毒没什么两样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.93,0:16:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是邪灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那块玉会玷污人的灵魂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些妖怪个个都\N带着假的四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.25,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳命来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出云先生\N你先带着那位小朋友躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.93,0:17:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走  往这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.68,0:17:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子比一般的妖怪更难对付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.52,0:17:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说是假货
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹多少也有\N四魂之玉的法力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很怀疑这些四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么样被做出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都什么时候了\N你还在想这些啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你们最好\N乖乖束手就擒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.03,0:17:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  还是要用风穴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  千万不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.05,0:18:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道事情会变成这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土蜘蛛  一角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.29,0:18:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为吞下几块假玉\N就可以增强妖力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.80,0:18:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出云先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.16,0:18:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.17,0:19:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.08,0:19:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的那些跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.28,0:19:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边  快追啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些灵魂看起来真美味儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.67,0:19:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我警告你最好别乱来\N蟾蜍次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.04,0:19:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在替我把\N小鬼的灵魂给弄出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.38,0:19:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.15,0:19:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就让你们一家团圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛王啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.69,0:19:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看先让你施展身手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的没问题吗犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.67,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近全部都是妖怪的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.17,0:20:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.84,0:20:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想四魂之玉\N就在正前方才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我感觉不是那么强烈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉的气息出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.26,0:20:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全都是假的四魂之玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.24,0:20:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.61,0:20:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊\N你这只愚蠢半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.38,0:20:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是半妖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瘴气…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.90,0:21:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.40,0:21:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太早得意忘形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.98,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连风之伤也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.91,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是四魂之玉的巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.02,0:21:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的灵魂如果没经过磨链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.65,0:21:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟普通的石头没什么两样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.42,0:21:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…他在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.52,0:22:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.70,0:22:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.98,0:22:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.39,0:22:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.73,0:22:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.33,0:22:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.01,0:23:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.25,0:23:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默承受伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.89,0:23:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.42,0:23:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.93,0:23:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.22,0:23:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲给我取的名字\N就叫做牛王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.79,0:23:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是你的“原料”?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.39,0:23:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你一直在骗我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.39,0:23:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂跟四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.13,0:23:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是新的四魂之玉的原料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.36,0:23:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过光是这些还不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必须补充灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.90,0:24:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要借四魂之玉的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.47,0:24:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让自己摆脱命运的控制才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.41,0:24:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.81,0:24:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉的伪造者 下集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.41,0:24:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界上最美的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.58,0:24:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部都要弄到手



